<p><a style="font-size:18px; line-height:22px; height:22px;" href="/shiwenv_d8f0f802885c.aspx"><b>君子阳阳</b></a></p>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a></p>
<div class="contson" id="contsond8f0f802885c">
君子阳阳，左执簧，右招我由房，其乐只且！<br />君子陶陶，左执翿，右招我由敖，其乐只且！
</div>
</div>
